et%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMyka%20Meier%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20share%20some%20of%20the%20most%20common%20missteps%20people%20make%20at%20work%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fis-the-cheesecake-factory-worth-it-chef-review-happy-hour-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehappy%20hours%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20how%20to%20avoid%20them.%20Here's%20what%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224f571ad2-ab47-46f4-89e5-22e8b0a4b404%5C%22%3EOverindulging%20in%20alcohol%20at%20happy%20hour%20can%20lead%20to%20issues%20in%20the%20workplace%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221219%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Three%20people%20clink%20cocktails%20together%20at%20a%20bar.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6705826e3f2165d716df5690%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22914%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDrinking%20too%20much%20can%20sometimes%20lead%20people%20to%20say%20things%20they%20wouldn't%20normally%20say%20in%20the%20workplace.%3Cp%3EPixelsEffect%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMeier%20said%20the%20biggest%20mistake%20people%20make%20when%20going%20to%20happy%20hour%20with%20their%20coworkers%20is%20overindulging%20in%20alcohol%20and%20not%20knowing%20their%20limits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20can%20be%20especially%20dangerous%20because%20drinking%20too%20much%20can%20sometimes%20lead%20people%20to%20say%20things%20they%20wouldn't%20normally%20say%20in%20the%20workplace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20say%20loose%20lips%20sink%20ships%2C%20and%20that%20ship%2C%20in%20this%20case%2C%20could%20be%20your%20career%2C%26quot%3B%20Meier%20said.%20%26quot%3BAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20with%20alcohol%2C%20we%20lose%20our%20inhibitions%20and%2C%20with%20that%2C%20our%20judgment.%20Sometimes%20we%20say%20things%20or%20do%20things%20we%20wouldn't%20usually%20do%20in%20a%20workplace.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20avoid%20making%20unprofessional%20comments%2C%20gossiping%2