gs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKnebeg's%20other%20major%20daily%20goal%20is%20to%20eat%20around%20142%20grams%20of%20protein.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecent%20evidence%20suggests%20that%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-much-protein-maximize-muscle-gains-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoptimal%20amount%20of%20protein%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%201.5%20grams%20per%20kilogram%20of%20body%20weight%20(or%200.7%20grams%20per%20pound)%20to%20maximize%20strength%20gains.%20The%20International%20Society%20of%20Sports%20Nutrition%20recommends%20between%201.4%20to%20two%20grams%20of%20protein%20per%20kilogram%20of%20body%20weight.%20More%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flow-protein-processed-food-leads-to-overeating-weight-gain-study-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprotein%20may%20help%20reduce%20cravings%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20a%20diet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHitting%20that%20goal%20doesn't%20have%20to%20involve%20intensive%20changes%20like%20chugging%20raw%20eggs%20after%20each%20workout%20or%20swapping%20in%20supplements%20for%20every%20meal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20bro%20science%20in%20the%20fitness%20community%2C%20particularly%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20men%2C%26quot%3B%20Enaz%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKnebeg%20said%20he%20included%20a%20lot%20more%20fish%20in%20his%20diet%20since%20it's%20a%20good%20source%20of%20protein%20and%20nutrients%20without%20many%20calories.%20He%20also%20ate%20more%20eggs%20and%20started%20snacking%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchickpeas-roasted-recipes-sweet-savory-delicious-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eroasted%20chickpeas%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20have%20the%20bonus%20of%20being%20high%20in%20fiber.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F30-10-rule-simple-diet-hack-eat-more-protein-dietitian-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efiber%20and%20protein%3C%