quot%3BDon't%20let%20them%20manipulate%20you%20into%20thinking%20that%20is%20being%20difficult%2C%20because%20I%20can%20look%20at%20that%20day%20and%20know%20I%20was%20a%2024-year-old%20kid%20who%20was%20raising%20concerns%20about%20how%20we%20were%20approaching%20things%2C%20and%20they%20were%20not%20listened%20to%2C%20they%20were%20not%20respected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20then%20what%20happened%20happened.%20And%20by%20all%20accounts%2C%20it%20was%20all%20pretty%20gotten%20away%20with%2C%20I%20would%20say%2C%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20life-changing%20incident.%20I've%20approached%20everything%20differently%2C%20you%20could%20say%2C%20particularly%20with%20regards%20to%20standing%20my%20ground%20on%20set.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20commonplace%20in%20the%20culture%20for%20young%20actors%20to%20be%20controlled%2C%20and%20the%20way%20they%20strive%20to%20do%20that%20is%20by%20always%20being%20like%2C%20'Oh%2C%20don't%20become%20difficult.%20Don't%20be%20a%20pain%20in%20the%20ass.%20Or%20Are%20you%20complaining%2C%20are%20you%20being%20difficult%3F'%20Things%20like%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Wes%20Ball%2C%20the%20director%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Maze%20Runner%3A%20The%20Death%20Cure%2C%26quot%3B%20and%2020th%20Century%20Studios%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20Business%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%20a%20number%20of%20incidents%20in%20recent%20years%20where%20stunts%20have%20gone%20wrong%20and%20severely%20injured%20or%20killed%20people%20on%20film%20sets.%20In%202021%2C%20actor%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falec-baldwin-shooting-rust-cinematographer-dead-timeline-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Alec%20Baldwin%20accidentally%20shot%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20killed%20cinematographer%20Halyna%20Hutchins%20while%20filming%20%26quot%3BRust.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20July%20