20at%20encouraging%20girls%20with%20a%20good%20academic%20record%20from%20families%20with%20an%20annual%20income%20of%20less%20than%20Rs%202.5%20lakh%20to%20pursue%20further%20studies%20in%20Classes%2011%20and%2012%20and%20college.%20To%20be%20eligible%2C%20the%20girls%20had%20to%20score%2065%25%20or%20more%20in%20the%20state%20board%20exams%20and%2075%25%20or%20more%20in%20the%20CBSE%20exams%20in%20Class%2010%20or%2012.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scooters%20have%20been%20parked%20on%20the%20grounds%20of%20the%20Vidyamandir%20College%20and%20the%20Hardev%20Joshi%20Government%20Girls%20College%20in%20Banswara%20since%202023%20and%20officials%20said%20the%20change%20in%20government%20late%20last%20year%20and%20the%20model%20code%20of%20conduct%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20have%20delayed%20their%20distribution.%20The%20BJP%20won%20the%20Assembly%20elections%20last%20year%20and%20took%20over%20from%20the%20Ashok%20Gehlot-led%20Congress%20government%2C%20under%20which%20the%20scheme%20was%20launched.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20girls%20apply%20for%20the%20scooters%2C%20a%20QR%20code%20is%20generated%20for%20each%20of%20them%20by%20the%20finance%20department%20after%20making%20sure%20that%20they%20meet%20the%20criteria.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20the%201%2C500%20scooters%2C%20the%20code%20has%20not%20been%20generated%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Sarla%20Pandya%2C%20principal%20of%20Hardev%20Joshi%20Government%20Girls%20College%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20the%20nodal%20college%20for%20distributing%20scooties%20under%20the%20welfare%20scheme.%20They%20were%20not%20distributed%20because%20of%20the%20model%20code%20of%20conduct%20and%20we%20are%20now%20awaiting%20a%20go-ahead%20from%20the%20finance%20department%20%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20has%20called%20it%20severe%20carelessness%20by%20the%20present%20government.%20Banswara%20MP%20Raj%20Kumar%20Roat%20of%20the%20Bharat%20Adivasi%20Party%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20criminal%20neglect%20by%20this%20government%2C%20the%20scooters%20are%20rusting%20and%20turning%20to%20scrap%20instead%20of%20reaching%20the%20beneficiaries.%20It%20is%20very%20sad%20that%20the%20government%20is%20not%20monitoring%20this%20situation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGovernment's%20Take%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20NDTV%20began%20making%20enquiries%2C%20the%20administration%20started%20pulling%20out%20the%20two-wheelers%20onto%20open%20ground%20and%20turning%20on%20the%20ignition%20to%20check%20if%20they%20were%20working.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajasthan%20Minister%20For%20Tribal%20Welfare%20Babu%20Lal%20Kharadi%20said%20the%20scooters%20would%20be%20distributed%20within%20a%20week%20but%20had%20no%20answer%20for%20why%20it%20took%20the%20new%20BJP%20government%20nearly%20a%20year%20to%20realise%20that%20they%20had%20remained%20parked.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BApproximately%203%2C000%20scooties%20were%20purchased%20in%202023%20and%201%2C500%20were%20distributed.%20This%20is%20a%20matter%20related%20to%20the%20previous%20government.%20There%20were%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20and%20then%20the%20Assembly%20session...%20we%20will%20ensure%20the%20scooters%20are%20distributed%20within%20a%20week%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kharadi%20also%20said%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20against%20officials%20for%20the%20neglect%20of%20government%20assets%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728651720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F2fcvk38o_rajasthan-scooters_625x300_11_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frajasthan-bought-1-500-scooters-for-girl-students-a-year-on-they-are-turning-to-scrap-6767860%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22More%20than%201%2C500%20brand%20new%20scooters%20purchased%20so%20that%20meritorious%20girls%20from%20poor%20families%20could%20continue%20their%20higher%20education%20are%20slowly%20turning%20to%20sc