atan%20Tata.%20(Photo%3A%20facebook%2FWelcometoJamshedpur)%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Ratan%20Tata%20and%20his%20half-brother%20Noel%20Tata%20with%20their%20father%20Naval%20Tata.%20Noel%20Tata%20is%2020%20years%20younger%20than%20Ratan%20Tata.%20(Photo%3A%20facebook%2FWelcometoJamshedpur)%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Ftduanp48_ratan-tata-and-noel-tata-with-father-naval-tata-facebook_625x300_11_October_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERatan%20Tata%20and%20his%20half-brother%20Noel%20Tata%20with%20their%20father%20Naval%20Tata.%20Noel%20Tata%20is%2020%20years%20younger%20than%20Ratan%20Tata.%20(Photo%3A%20facebook%2FWelcometoJamshedpur)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETHE%20TATA%20FAMILY%20ANCESTRY%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAncestors%20of%20the%20Tata%20family%20migrated%20to%20India%20from%20Persia%2C%20now%20Iran%2C%20in%20the%208th%20century%20AD.%20They%20were%20part%20of%20a%20large%20group%20of%20Parsis%20(people%20from%20Persia)%2C%20a%20Zoroastrian%20ethnic%20community%2C%20who%20fled%20persecution%20during%20the%20Islamic%20Conquest%20of%20Persia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Tata%20Central%20Archives%2C%20the%20Tatas%20settled%20in%20Navsari%20in%20Gujarat%20and%20lived%20there%20for%2025%20generations%20before%20business%20took%20them%20to%20Bombay%20-%20then%20the%20Bombay%20Presidency%20under%20the%20British%20Raj.%20At%20the%20time%20Bombay%20Province%20included%20the%20western%20two-thirds%20of%20Maharashtra%2C%20northwestern%20Karnataka%2C%20all%20of%20Gujarat%2C%20all%20of%20Sindh%20(now%20in%20Pakistan)%2C%20and%20Aden%20(in%20present-day%20Yemen).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20journey%20of%20the%20Tata%20family's%20business%20began%20with%20Jamsetji%20Nusserwanji%20Tata%2C%20who%20stated%20a%20trading%20company%20in%20Bombay%20in%201868%2C%20which%20has%20today%20become%20the%20Tata%20Group.%20The%20Tatas%20have%20always%20believed%20in%20the%20concept%20of%20country%20and%20society%20-%20building%20and%20uplifting%20the%20people%20and%20the%20community%20over%20personal%20gains%20-%20and%20right%20from%20the%20very%20beginning%2C%20Jamsetji%20and%20his%20two%20sons%20-%20Sir%20Dorabji%20Tata%20and%20Sir%20Ratan%20Tata%20-%20left%20most%20of%20their%20estate%20and%20shares%20in%20the%20company%20to%20charitable%20trusts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Tata%20family%20moved%20from%20Persia%20to%20India%20in%20the%208th%20Century%20and%20settled%20in%20Gujarat.%20Jamsetji%20Tata%20founded%20the%20business%20in%201868.%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22The%20Tata%20family%20moved%20from%20Persia%20to%20India%20in%20the%208th%20Century%20and%20settled%20in%20Gujarat.%20Jamsetji%20Tata%20founded%20the%20business%20in%201868.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F8j6niovs_ratan-tata-and-noel-tata-with-their-father-naval-tata_625x300_11_October_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Tata%20family%20moved%20from%20Persia%20to%20India%20in%20the%208th%20Century%20and%20settled%20in%20Gujarat.%20Jamsetji%20Tata%20founded%20the%20business%20in%201868.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20there%20are%2014%20different%20trusts%20run%20by%20the%20Tatas%20which%20work%20in%20different%20sectors%2C%20each%20independent%20of%20the%20other%20in%20the%20nature%20and%20field%20of%20work%20they%20do.%20All%20of%20these%20however%2C%20come%20under%20an%20umbrella%20organisation%20called%20Tata%20Trust.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fratan-tatas-journey-from-mumbai-boy-to-the-global-icon-a-timeline-of-his-life-6756202%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERatan%20Tata%20was%20the%20Chairman%20of%20the%20Tata%20Trusts%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Chairman%20Emeritus%20of%20the%20Tata%20Group.%20After%20his%20demise%2C%20his%20half-brother%20Noel%20Tata%20has%20become%20the%20Chairman%20of%20Tata%20Trusts%20while%20Natarajan%20Chandrasekaran%20is%20Chairman%20of%20the%20Tata%20Group%2C%20who