cheduled%20to%20be%20held%20on%20October%2022-24%20in%20Kazan%2C%20most%20eagerly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20he%20skipped%20the%20summit%20in%20South%20Africa%20for%20fear%20of%20being%20arrested.%20In%20March%202023%2C%20the%20International%20Criminal%20Court%20(ICC)%20issued%20an%20arrest%20warrant%20for%20Putin%20over%20alleged%20war%20crimes%20committed%20during%20Russia's%20full-scale%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine.%20South%20Africa%2C%20as%20a%20signatory%20to%20the%20Rome%20Statute%2C%20would%20have%20been%20obligated%20to%20arrest%20him%20had%20he%20entered%20the%20country.%20And%20so%2C%20Putin%20had%20to%20make%20do%20with%20virtual%20participation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20year's%20BRICS%20summit%20will%20be%20a%20significant%20moment%20for%20him%20as%20he%20will%20not%20only%20host%20the%20event%20on%20his%20own%20turf%20but%20he%20will%20also%20be%20keen%20to%20show%20to%20the%20Western%20world%20that%20despite%20their%20sanctions%20on%20Russia%20and%20attempts%20to%20diplomatically%20isolate%20him%2C%20he%20is%20still%20playing%20host%20to%20some%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20influential%20leaders%2C%20such%20as%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping.%20As%20a%20host%2C%20Putin's%20effort%20will%20be%20to%20highlight%20Russia's%20successful%20outreach%20to%20non-Western%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20true%20that%20despite%20Western%20sanctions%2C%20Russia%20remains%20a%20pivotal%20member%20of%20this%20dynamic%20group%2C%20which%20represents%2024%25%20of%20the%20global%20nominal%20GDP%20and%2041%25%20of%20the%20world's%20population.%20Despite%20attempts%20to%20isolate%20Russia%20following%20its%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%2C%20Putin%20may%20also%20claim%20that%20Moscow%20remains%20a%20key%20player%20in%20reshaping%20the%20world%20order%2C%20drawing%20strength%20from%20its%20BRICS%20alliances.%20These%20ties%20illustrate%20how%20countries%20outside%20the%20G7%20are%20increasingly%20seeking%20alternatives%20to%20Western-dominated%20institutions%20like%20the%20International%20Monetary%20Fund%20(IMF)%20and%20the%20World%20Bank%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3EBRICS%20Is%20Here%20To%20Stay%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBRICS%2C%20the%20economic%20and%20political%20alliance%20comprising%20Brazil%2C%20Russia%2C%20India%2C%20China%20and%20South%20Africa%2C%20has%20gained%20a%20lot%20of%20prominence%20since%20its%20inception%2015%20years%20ago.%20Political%20analysts%2C%20economists%20and%20academics%20in%20the%20West%20had%20long%20predicted%20its%20demise.%20For%20instance%2C%20Eurasia%20Group%2C%20a%20political%20risk%20consultancy%2C%20questioned%20BRICS'%20relevance%20in%202013%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BBRICS%20is%20a%20term%20that%20has%20lost%20its%20relevance...%20It's%20a%20grouping%20that%20doesn't%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20coherence%2C%20and%20it's%20not%20clear%20what%20they%20are%20trying%20to%20achieve%20together.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20has%20not%20just%20endured%20but%20is%20expanding%2C%20defying%20initial%20Western%20scepticism.%20Its%20latest%20members%20are%20Iran%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20Egypt%2C%20Ethiopia%20and%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates.%20The%20bloc%20has%20attracted%20interest%20from%20nearly%2040%20other%20countries%2C%20including%20NATO%20member%20Turkey%2C%20which%20has%20now%20formally%20applied%20for%20its%20membership.%20Indonesia%20has%20been%20invited%20to%20join%20too%2C%20but%20it%20seems%20to%20be%20reluctant%20to%20become%20a%20part%20of%20the%20group%2C%20which%2C%20it%20views%20as%20anti-West.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia%20Should%20Carve%20Out%20Its%20Own%20Playing%20Field%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20years%20after%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20was%20founded%20in%201885%2C%20it%20remained%20a%20petitioner%20to%20the%20British%20Raj.%20The%20assertion%20of%20its%20right%20to%20self-determination%20was%20weak%20until%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20arrived%20on%20the%20national%20landscape.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20India%20should%20not%20be%20seen%20to%20be%20petitioning%20for%20a%20permanent%20seat%20on%20the%20United%20Nations%20Security%20Council%20(UNSC).%20The%20UN%20and%20UNSC%2C%20formed%20after%20the%20Second%20World%20War%2C%20are%20relics%20of%20the%2020th%20century.%20The%20global%20landscape%20has%20dramatically%20changed%20since%20then%2C%20with%20emerging%20economies%20like%20India%20yearning%20to%20play%20a%20far%20more%20significant%20role%20in%20global%20affairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20world's%20most%20populous%20country%2C%20the%20fifth-largest%20economy%20and%20a%20robust%20democracy%20to%20boot%2C%20Indians%20believe%20they%20should%20have%20a%20permanent%20voice%20in%20the%20decision-making%20processes%20that%20affect%20global%20peace%20and%20security.%20But%20the%20US%2C%20often%20in%20collaboration%20with%20its%20Western%20allies%2C%20has%20considerable%20sway%20within%20the%20UN%20system%2C%20which%20allows%20it%20to%20exert%20influence%20over%20its%20priorities%20and%20decision-making.%20The%20US%20is%20so%20powerful%20that%20it%20has%20managed%20to%20restrict%20BRICS's%20progress%20too.%20For%20example%2C%20many%20Chinese%20banks%20have%20ceased%20transactions%20with%20Russia%20to%20avoid%20US%20penalties%2C%20and%20BRICS's%20New%20Development%20Bank%20(NDB)%20has%20frozen%20its%20projects%20in%20Russia%20due%20to%20US%20sanctions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20government%20is%20not%20necessarily%20in%20favour%20of%20dismantling%20the%20existing%20US-led%20world%20order.%20It%20argues%20that%20the%20system%20has%20to%20be%20more%20inclusive%3B%20it%20wants%20what%20it%20believes%20are%20its%20rights%20in%20the%20existing%20system.%20It%20urges%20reforms%20in%20global%20financial%20institutions%2C%20such%20as%20the%20International%20Monetary%20Fund%20(IMF)%20and%20the%20World%20Bank%2C%20which%20further%20highlights%20its%20desire%20for%20a%20more%20equitable%20distribution%20of%20power%20in%20the%20global%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWest%20'Protecting'%20The%20Existing%20Order%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%2C%20France%20and%20the%20UK%2C%20all%20three%20permanent%20members%20of%20the%20UNSC%2C%20have%20often%20openly%20supported%20India's%20stance%20on%20the%20reform%20of%20international%20bodies.%20But%20it's%20unclear%20how%20genuine%20their%20intentions%20are.%20With%20the%20war%20raging%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20West%20Asia%20engulfed%20in%20violence%20and%20China's%20rise%20as%20their%20global%20challenger%2C%20the%20US%20and%20its%20Western%20allies%20appear%20to%20have%20become%20more%20assertive%20to%20protect%20their%20dominance%20of%20the%20world%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20India%2C%20the%20time%20for%20petitioning%20or%20expecting%20favours%20from%20the%20West%20without%20a%20quid%20pro%20quo%20is%20over.%20India%20should%20use%20BRICS%20as%20a%20platform%20for%20amplifying%20its%20voice%20in%20global%20governance.%20It%20should%20value%20BRICS%20as%20a%20platform%20to%20advocate%20for%20a%20multipolar%20world.%20This%20is%20not%20to%20suggest%20that%20New%20Delhi%20should%20allow%20BRICS%20to%20become%20an%20overtly%20anti-West%20group.%20But%20it%20should%20use%20the%20platform%20to%20its%20advantage.%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20often%20talked%20about%20India's%20ambition%20to%20be%20a%20leading%20voice%20of%20the%20Global%20South.%20Global%20bodies%2C%20such%20as%20BRICS%20and%20G20%2C%20provide%20a%20means%20to%20achieve%20such%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Does%20China%20Have%20The%20Upper%20Hand%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20benefited%20economically%20from%20the%20group%2C%20particularly%20through%20discounted%20Russian%20energy%20imports%20amid%20Western%20sanctions.%20Being%20a%20founding%20member%20of%20BRICS%2C%20India%20should%20realise%20that%20global%20fora%20such%20as%20BRICS%20and%20the%20G20%20are%20credible%20products%20of%20a%20new%2C%20multipolar%20international%20order.%20If%20you%20do%20not%20get%20your%20rightful%20place%20in%20the%20existing%20order%2C%20you%20help%20create%20a%20new%20one%2C%20a%20more%20just%20order%2C%20without%20disengaging%20yourself%20with%20the%20existing%20one.%20India's%20increasing%20engagement%20in%20BRICS%20and%20the%20G20%20demonstrates%20its%20willingness%20to%20work%20within%20the%20existing%20global%20order%20while%20advocating%20for%20change%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20should%20go%20a%20step%20further%20and%20be%20an%20agent%20of%20change.%20It%20should%20not%20allow%20China%20to%20control%20the%20BRICS%20agenda.%20But%20sadly%2C%20even%20though%20India%20is%20a%20founding%20member%2C%20it%20does%20not%20wield%20as%20much%20direct%20influence%20as%20China%2C%20mostly%20due%20to%20the%20latter's%20economic%20and%20geopolitical%20clout.%20Russia%2C%20despite%20sanctions%2C%20remains%20a%20key%20BRICS%20player%2C%20especially%20because%20it%20sees%20the%20group%20as%20a%20way%20to%20counterbalance%20Western%20influence.%20But%20India's%20importance%20within%20the%20group%20is%20undisputed%20in%20some%20areas.%20For%20example%2C%20it%20brings%20credibility%20to%20the%20bloc%20because%20of%20its%20democratic%20credentials.%20It%20is%20an%20established%20global%20player%20in%20the%20IT%20sector%20and%20a%20huge%20market%20for%20investment.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20The%20West%20Thinks%20Of%20BRICS%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20in%20the%20West%20now%20appear%20to%20take%20BRICS%20quite%20seriously%20as%20a%20counterbalance%20to%20the%20Western%20hegemony.%20But%20they%20suspect%20that%20the%20inherent%20division%20within%20the%20group%20could%20hamper%20its%20progress%20into%20a%20true%20alternative%20to%20the%20West-dominated%20world%20order.%20China%20and%20Russia%20are%20pushing%20BRICS%20to%20become%20a%20decidedly%20anti-West%20bloc.%20The%20recent%20inclusion%20of%20anti-West%20Iran%2C%20at%20their%20behest%2C%20is%20a%20case%20in%20point.%20Indeed%2C%20experts%20in%20the%20West%20believe%20that%20the%20alliance%20seeks%20alternative%20centres%20of%20power%2C%20frustrated%20with%20Western%20domination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%2C%20China%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20create%20an%20alternative%20global%20financial%20and%20technological%20system%20to%20circumvent%20the%20US%20dollar%20dominance.%20Projects%20such%20as%20the%20Belt%20and%20Road%20Initiative%20(BRI)%2C%20the%20creation%20of%20the%20New%20Development%20Bank%20(NDB)%20and%20efforts%20to%20internationalise%20the%20Yuan%20align%20with%20Chinese%20goals%20of%20establishing%20an%20alternative%20multipolar%20world%20order.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20India%2C%20South%20Africa%20and%20Brazil%20do%20not%20fully%20share%20China's%20ambitions.%20They%20favour%20reforming%20the%20existing%20global%20system%20rather%20than%20dismantling%20it.%20They%20aim%20for%20a%20multipolar%20world%20where%20they%20can%20balance%20relations%20between%20the%20US%20and%20China%2C%20without%20fully%20aligning%20with%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20question%20of%20whether%20BRICS%20can%20maintain%20its%20cohesion%20amid%20internal%20divisions%20looms%20large%20over%20the%20Kazan%20summit.%20I%20will%20be%20keenly%20observing%20how%20the%20summit%20navigates%20its%20members'%20competing%20national%20interests.%20But%20what%20one%20can%20say%20with%20confidence%20is%20that%20the%20group's%20relevance%20as%20a%20counterweight%20to%20Western%20power%20is%20indisputable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Syed%20Zubair%20Ahmed%20is%20a%20London-based%20senior%20Indian%20journalist%20with%20three%20decades%20of%20experience%20with%20the%20Western%20media)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728648480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fv6ngbbqo_bircs_625x