quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThey%20help%20us%20to%20describe%20the%20indescribable%2C%20to%20think%20the%20unthinkable%2C%20and%20to%20somehow%20grasp%20the%20incomprehensible%20pain%20and%20suffering%20caused%20by%20nuclear%20weapons%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20committee%20stated%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20also%20highlighted%20that%20no%20nuclear%20weapon%20has%20been%20used%20in%20war%20in%20nearly%2080%20years.%20Acknowledging%C2%A0Nihon%20Hidankyo's%20efforts%20towards%20the%20establishment%20of%20a%20nuclear%20taboo%2C%20the%20Nobel%20Committee%20also%20aid%20that%20the%20same%20is%20under%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%C2%A0drawing%20on%20personal%20stories%2C%20creating%20educational%20campaigns%20based%20on%20their%20own%20experience%2C%20and%20issuing%20urgent%20warnings%20against%20the%20spread%20and%20use%20of%20nuclear%20weapons%2C%20the%20organisation%20has%20helped%20consolidate%20opposition%20to%20nuclear%20weapons%2C%20said%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nobelprize.org%2Fpress-release-peace-2024%2F%5C%22%3ENobel%20Committee%20press%20release%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20nuclear%20powers%20are%20modernising%20and%20upgrading%20their%20arsenals%2C%20new%20countries%20appear%20to%20be%20preparing%20to%20acquire%20nuclear%20weapons%2C%20and%20threats%20are%20being%20made%20to%20use%20nuclear%20weapons%20in%20ongoing%20warfare.%20At%20this%20moment%20in%20human%20history%2C%20it%20is%20worth%20reminding%20ourselves%20what%20nuclear%20weapons%20are%3A%20the%20most%20destructive%20weapons%20the%20world%20has%20ever%20seen%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20press%20release%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%202024%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnobel-prize-in-chemistry-goes-to-scientists-david-baker-demis-hassabis-john-jumper-6751373%5C%22%3ENobel%20Prize%20in%20Chemistry%3C%2Fa%3E%20went%20to%20scientists%20David%20Baker%2C%20Demis%20Hassabis%20and%20John%20Jumper%2C%20while%20the%C2%A