2author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnobel-peace-prize-2024-goes-to-japanese-organisation-nihon-hidankyo-6766192%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Why%20Farm%20Protests%20Made%20Little%20Impact%20On%20Haryana%20Elections%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.gadgets360cdn.com%2Flarge%2Ffarmers_protest_reuters_1612349909888.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20lead-up%20to%20the%20recently%20concluded%20Haryana%20assembly%20elections%2C%20anti-incumbency%20sentiment%20was%20expected%20to%20surge%2C%20fuelled%20by%20farmers'%20protests%20and%20other%20significant%20issues%20weighing%20on%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP).%20The%20Congress%20banked%20heavily%20on%20the%20unrest%20among%20farmers%2C%20wrestlers'%20protests%2C%20and%20caste%20divisions%20to%20build%20a%20narrative%20that%20seemed%20poised%20to%20propel%20the%20party%20to%20the%20top%20of%20the%20state's%20political%20landscape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20election%20results%20told%20a%20different%20story.%20So%2C%20how%20much%20impact%20did%20the%20protesting%20farmers%20have%20on%20the%20assembly%20elections%3F%20In%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20the%20Congress%20saw%20an%20increase%20in%20both%20the%20number%20of%20seats%20and%20vote%20share%20in%20Haryana%2C%20largely%20attributed%20to%20the%20farmers'%20discontent%20with%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20years%20ago%2C%20when%20a%20coalition%20of%20peasant%20organisations%20successfully%20forced%20the%20rollback%20of%20three%20controversial%20farm%20laws%2C%20it%20was%20perceived%20as%20a%20significant%20blow%20to%20the%20Narendra%20Modi-led%20Union%20government.%20The%20euphoria%20of%20this%20so-called%20victory%20among%20farmer%20leaders%20soon%20transitioned%20into%20a%20political%20campaign%20against%20the%20BJP.%20Although%20their%20demands%2C%20including%20the%20legalisation%20of%20the%20Minimum%20Support%20Price%20(MSP)%2C%20remained%20a%20focus%2C%20the%20protests%20took%20on%20an%20increasingly%20political%20tone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Mixed%20Outcome%20For%20Farmers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Haryana%20assembly%20results%20revealed%20a%20mixed%20outcome%20for%20the%20protesting%20farmers.%20While%20the%20BJP's%20popularity%20appeared%20to%20dip%20after%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20results%2C%20the%20assembly%20election%20results%20signalled%20a%20change.%20Initially%2C%20the%20protesters%20succeeded%20in%20shaping%20the%20narrative.%20From%20staging%20pickets%20against%20BJP%20leaders%20during%20campaigns%20to%20public%20outreach%20and%20demonstrations%2C%20the%20farm%20leaders%20left%20no%20stone%20unturned.%20Protests%20at%20administrative%20offices%20and%20toll%20plazas%20further%20reinforced%20their%20message%2C%20but%20the%20overall%20mandate%20suggests%20their%20efforts%20had%20limited%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGurnam%20Singh%20Charuni%2C%20a%20prominent%20farmer%20leader%20who%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20the%20protests%20against%20the%20now-repealed%20farm%20laws%2C%20managed%20to%20secure%20only%201%2C170%20votes%20in%20Pehowa%2C%20finishing%20fifth.%20The%20seat%20was%20won%20by%20Mandeep%20Chatha%20of%20the%20Congress%2C%20who%20defeated%20BJP's%20Jai%20Bhagwan%20Sharma%20by%20more%20than%206%2C500%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECharuni%2C%2064%2C%20who%20has%20faced%20multiple%20imprisonments%20since%201992%20due%20to%20his%20activism%2C%20is%20the%20president%20of%20a%20faction%20of%20the%20Bhartiya%20Kisan%20Union.%20He%20contested%20the%20election%20under%20his%20political%20party%2C%20the%20Sanyukt%20Sangharsh%20Party%20(SSP).%20It%20is%20said%20that%20Charuni%20was%20initially%20seeking%20a%20Congress%20ticket%20to%20challenge%20the%20BJP%20but%20decided%20to%20contest%20independently%20when%20that%20didn't%20materialise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%2C%20state%20BJP%20leader%20and%20former%20Haryana%20minister%20Anil%20Vij%20managed%20to%20retain%20the%20Ambala%20Cantonment%20constituency%20despite%20facing%20significant%20farmer%20protests.%20He%20defeated%20independent%20candidate%20Chitra%20Sarwara%2C%20a%20former%20member%20of%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%2C%20by%20over%207%2C000%20votes%2C%20with%20Congress%20candidate%20Parvinder%20Pal%20Pari%20trailing%20in%20third%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVij%20-%20who%20was%20dropped%20from%20the%20cabinet%20when%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar%20was%20replaced%20as%20chief%20minister%20by%20Nayab%20Singh%20Saini%20in%20March%20-%20was%20heavily%20targeted%20by%20farmer%20unions%20throughout%20his%20campaign.%20They%20picketed%20his%20election%20rallies%2C%20and%20protests%20followed%20his%20campaign%20trail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20Hisar%20and%20Ratia%2C%20where%20BJP%20candidates%20also%20faced%20intense%20protests%20over%20farm%20issues%2C%20the%20party%20suffered%20losses.%20In%20Hisar%2C%20BJP%20leader%20Kamal%20Gupta%20finished%20third%2C%20while%20in%20Ratia%2C%20Sunita%20Duggal%20lost%20to%20Congress%20candidate%20Jarnail%20Singh%20by%20over%2021%2C000%20votes.%20Gupta%20had%20previously%20won%20the%20Hisar%20seat%20in%20both%20the%202014%20and%202019%20assembly%20elections.%20In%20Ratia%2C%20sitting%20BJP%20legislator%20Lakshman%20Dass%20Napa%20quit%20the%20party%20after%20being%20denied%20a%20ticket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Border%20Impact%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20constituencies%20bordering%20Punjab%20-%20a%20state%20that%20strongly%20rejected%20the%20BJP%20and%20has%20a%20robust%20base%20of%20farm%20unions%20-%20the%20election%20results%20were%20more%20polarised.%20Congress%20secured%20nine%20seats%2C%20while%20the%20BJP%20won%20three.%20Of%20these%2C%20the%20BJP%20managed%20to%20retain%20one%20but%20lost%20five%20to%20the%20Congress.%20The%20Congress%20kept%20two%20seats%20but%20lost%20one%20to%20the%20BJP.%20Dushyant%20Chautala's%20Jannayak%20Janta%20Party%20(JJP)%2C%20which%20was%20once%20allied%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20lost%20the%20two%20seats%20it%20previously%20held%20in%20the%20Punjab%20border%20region%20-%20one%20to%20Congress%20and%20the%20other%20to%20the%20BJP.%20Notably%2C%20the%20JJP%20failed%20to%20win%20a%20single%20seat%20in%20this%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFarm%20Politics%20And%20Political%20Leanings%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20many%20Samyukta%20Kisan%20Morcha%20(SKM)%20leaders%20being%20directly%20connected%20with%20anti-BJP%20parties%2C%20the%20group%20largely%20stayed%20out%20of%20the%20elections.%20In%202022%2C%20the%20SKM%20severed%20ties%20with%20the%20Samyukta%20Samaj%20Morcha%20(SSM)%20led%20by%20Balbir%20Singh%20Rajewal%20and%20Charuni's%20SSP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20poster%20boy%20of%20the%202020-2021%20anti-farm%20law%20protests%2C%20Rakesh%20Tikait%2C%20previously%20contested%20elections%2C%20but%20without%20success.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Hannan%20Mollah%2C%20a%20senior%20leader%20of%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22All%20India%20Kisan%20Sabha%20(36%20Canning%20Lane)%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FAll_India_Kisan_Sabha_(36_Canning_Lane)%5C%22%3EAll%20India%20Kisan%20Sabha%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20former%20member%20of%20Parliament%20from%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)%2C%20won%20from%20West%20Bengal's%20Uluberia%20eight%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20political%20leanings%20of%20most%20SKM%20leaders%20are%20rooted%20in%20socialist%20or%20Left%20ideologies%20-%20traditionally%20anti-BJP.%20However%2C%20the%20peasant%20leaders%20likely%20missed%20a%20critical%20lesson%20from%202020%20when%2C%20during%20the%20height%20of%20the%20protests%2C%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20won%20a%20majority%20in%20the%20Bihar%20assembly%20elections%2C%20despite%20the%20anti-farm%20law%20sentiment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUndeterred%2C%20farm%20leaders%20continued%20to%20campaign%20against%20the%20BJP%20in%20subsequent%20state%20elections.%20While%20the%20BJP%20won%20governments%20in%20Assam%20and%20Puducherry%2C%20other%20parties%20triumphed%20in%20states%20like%20Kerala%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20and%20West%20Bengal%2C%20where%20SKM%20leaders%20claimed%20some%20credit%20for%20the%20electoral%20outcomes%2C%20particularly%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20where%20Mamata%20Banerjee's%20Trinamool%20Congress%20scored%20a%20major%20victory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20these%20efforts%2C%20two%20years%20later%20it%20seems%20that%20while%20farm-related%20issues%20may%20have%20influenced%20voters%20in%20border%20areas%2C%20they%20failed%20to%20swing%20the%20overall%20mandate%20away%20from%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Jayanta%20Bhattacharya%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%20writing%20on%20polls%20and%20politics%2C%20conflict%2C%20farmer%20and%20human%20interest%20issues)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728639540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.gadgets360cdn.com%2Flarge%2Ffarmers_protest_reuters_1612349909888.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhy-farm-protests-made-little-impact-on-haryana-elections-6766193%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Two%20years%20later%20it%20seems%20that%20while%20farm-related%20issues%20may%20have%20influenced%20voters%20in%20border%20areas%20of%20Haryana%2C%20they%20failed%20to%20swing%20the%20overall%20mandate%20away%20from%20the%20BJP.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhy-farm-protests-made-little-impact-on-haryana-elections-6766193%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%