diatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fjigra-x-review-alia-bhatt-is-impressive-fans-praise-vasan-balas-direction-but-say-the-story-lacks-depth%2Farticleshow%2F114143692.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F114143692.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Jigra%E2%80%99%20starring%20Alia%20Bhatt%20and%20Vedang%20Raina%20hit%20theaters%20on%20October%2011.%20Directed%20by%20Vasan%20Bala%2C%20the%20film%20explores%20a%20sister's%20determination%20to%20protect%20her%20brother.%20The%20movie%20has%20received%20mixed%20reviews%20on%20social%20media%2C%20praising%20Alia%20Bhatt%E2%80%99s%20performance%20but%20finding%20some%20issues%20with%20the%20screenplay%20and%20music.%20It%20faces%20box%20office%20competition%20from%20another%20film.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fjigra-x-review-alia-bhatt-is-impressive-fans-praise-vasan-balas-direction-but-say-the-story-lacks-depth%2Farticleshow%2F114143692.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Juice%20Seller%20To%20Millionaire%20Scammer%3A%20Mahadev%20Betting%20App%20Accused's%20Empire%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20Indian%20authorities%20prepare%20to%20likely%20receive%20Saurabh%20Chandrakar%2C%20one%20of%20the%20main%20promoters%20of%20the%20Mahadev%20betting%20app%2C%20sources%20told%20NDTV%20how%20the%20money%20was%20moved%20around%2C%20the%20extent%20of%20the%20nexus%20involved%20in%20the%20operation%20of%20the%20app%20and%20the%20titular%20role%20of%20two%20Chhattisgarh-based%20brothers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20sources%2C%20Chandrakar's%20formal%20arrest%20in%20the%20Dubai%20was%20based%20on%20an%20Interpol-issued%20arrest%20warrant%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20and%20fraud%20case.%20Chandrakar%20along%20with%20another%20promoter%20of%20the%20app%2C%20Ravi%20Uppal%20was%20detained%20and%20put%20under%20%26quot%3Bhouse%20arrest%26quot%3B%20in%20Dubai%20late%20last%20year%20following%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate's%20(ED)%20request%20for%20issuance%20of%20a%20Red%20Notice%20(RN)%20against%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandrakar%20and%20co-promoter%20Ravil%20Uppal%20hailed%20from%20Chhattisgarh's%20Bhilai%2C%20but%20operated%20the%20Mahadev%20betting%20app%20from%20Dubai.%20When%20he%20lived%20in%20his%20hometown%2C%20the%20former%20ran%20a%20juice%20shop.%20He%20is%20said%20to%20have%20left%20for%20Dubai%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20starting%20the%20app%2C%20the%20duo%20opened%20call%20centres%20in%20major%20cities%20of%20Malaysia%2C%20Thailand%2C%20UAE%20and%20India%20through%20which%20various%20subsidiary%20apps%20were%20made%20to%20facilitate%20online%20betting.%20In%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20other%20states%20of%20India%2C%20around%2030%20call%20centres%20were%20being%20operated%20with%20the%20help%20of%20two%20persons%2C%20identified%20as%20Sunil%20Damani%20and%20Anil%20Damani%2C%20both%20close%20aides%20of%20Chandrakar%20and%20Uppal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20has%20claimed%20the%20network%20consisted%20of%20around%204%2C000%20'panel%20operators'%2C%20based%20across%20different%20states%20in%20India%2C%20with%20handling%20around%20200%20customers%20placing%20bets.%20Using%20this%20method%2C%20the%20two%20made%20at%20least%20%E2%82%B9%20200%20crore%20daily%2C%20and%20managed%20to%20build%20a%20criminal%20empire%20in%20the%20UAE.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInvestigation%20by%20the%20ED%20found%20that%20thousand%20of%20crores%20were%20swindled%20through%20the%20betting%20and%20other%20interlinked%20apps%2C%20according%20to%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20money%20trail%20of%20a%20deep-running%20nexus%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandrakar%20and%20Uppal%2C%20along%20with%20the%20police%2C%20bureaucrats%20and%20politicians%20operated%20a%20nexus%20to%20run%20the%20app%20and%20manage%20its%20proceeds%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20help%20from%20the%20Damanis%2C%20a%20large%20number%20of%20benami%20bank%20accounts%20were%20opened.%20Anil%20Damani%20was%20entrusted%20with%20rerouting%20the%20money%20obtained%20through%20hawala%20to%20pay%20the%20police%2C%20politicians%20and%20bureaucrats%20to%20avoid%20coming%20under%20the%20scanner.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoney%20was%20also%20sent%20to%20Chandra%20Bhushan%20Verma%2C%20an%20Assistant%20Sub%20Inspector%20with%20Chhattisgarh%20Police%2C%20for%20the%20same%20purpose.%20He%20was%20in%20direct%20contact%20with%20Vinod%20Verma%2C%20the%20political%20advisor%20of%20then%20Chhattisgarh%20CM%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%2C%20with%20whose%20support%20he%20was%20managing%20the%20syndicate%20of%20police%2C%20bureaucrats%20and%20politicians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Damanis%20also%20sent%20large%20sums%20of%20cash%20to%20the%20promoters%20in%20UAE%20through%20hawala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20questioning%2C%20Anil%20Damani%20said%20that%20in%20the%20last%202-3%20years%2C%20Sunil%20Damani%20and%20he%20carried%20out%20transactions%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20Rs%2060-65%20crore%20through%20hawala%20on%20the%20request%20of%20Uppal%2C%20while%20he%20was%20given%20Rs%206%20lakh.%20He%20added%20that%20they%20run%20the%20hawala%20ring%20through%20their%20jewellery%20shop.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECall%20Detail%20Records%20show%20the%20Damanis%20have%20been%20in%20constant%20contact%20with%20Chandrakar%20and%20Uppal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESatish%20Chandrakar%2C%20who%20was%20arrested%20in%20this%20case%20by%20the%20ED%2C%20was%20running%20four%20call%20centres%20and%20had%20a%20five%20percent%20stake.%20He%20too%20was%20tasked%20with%20overseeing%20the%20illegal%20money%20transactions.%20Probe%20also%20revealed%20that%20Satish%20Chandrakar%20was%20also%20connected%20to%20gangster%20and%20drug%20mafia%20boss%20Tapan%20Sarkar%2C%20who%20is%20on%20the%20run%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20projected%20proceeds%20of%20crime%20in%20this%20case%20are%20about%20Rs%206%2C000%20crore%2C%20according%20to%20the%20ED.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Bollywood%20connection%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20has%20alleged%20in%20its%20charge%20sheet%20that%20Chandrakar%20got%20married%20at%20UAE's%20Ras%20Al%20Khaimah%20in%20February%202023%20and%20about%20Rs%20200%20crore%20%26quot%3Bin%20cash%26quot%3B%20was%20spent%20for%20this%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%2017%20Hindi%20film%20celebrities%20and%20Chandrakar's%20relatives%20were%20flown%20in%20by%20chartered%20flights.%20The%20celebrities%20also%20performed%20at%20the%20wedding%20and%20were%20allegedly%20paid%20crores%20of%20rupees%20through%20hawala%20in%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20actor%20Ranbir%20Kapoor%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20promoting%20a%20sporting%20app%20linked%20to%20the%20Mahadev%20online%20betting%20app.%20Hence%2C%20all%20actors%20who%20were%20present%20at%20the%20wedding%20have%20been%20included%20in%20the%20scope%20of%20the%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728634980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fvifqiacg_mahadev-betting-app-accused-_625x300_11_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmahadev-betting-app-case-how-promoters-moved-money-kept-illegal-actions-away-from-govt-scanner-6765593%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Saurabh%20Chandrakar%20and%20co-promoter%20Ravil%20Uppal%20hailed%20from%20Chhattisgarhs%20Bhilai%2C%20but%20operated%20the%20Mahadev%20betting%20app%20from%20Dubai.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmahadev-betting-app-case-how-promoters-moved-money-kept-illegal-actions-away-from-govt-scanner-6765593%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Body%20Of%20Missing%20Pil