a%20on%20childhood%20sexual%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unicef.org%2Fpress-releases%2Fover-370-million-girls-and-women-globally-subjected-rape-or-sexual-assault-children%5C%22%3E%20report%20highlights%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20when%20%26quot%3Bnon-contact%26quot%3B%20forms%20of%20abuse%20-%20such%20as%20online%20harassment%20or%20verbal%20assault%20-%20are%20factored%20in%2C%20the%20number%20rises%20to%20650%20million%2C%20or%201%20in%205.%20The%20staggering%20statistics%20underscore%20the%20critical%20need%20for%20urgent%20and%20comprehensive%20strategies%20to%20prevent%20and%20address%20the%20widespread%20violation%20of%20children's%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSexual%20violence%20against%20children%20is%20a%20stain%20on%20our%20moral%20conscience%2C%26quot%3B%20stated%20UNICEF%20Executive%20Director%20Catherine%20Russell.%20%26quot%3BIt%20inflicts%20deep%20and%20lasting%20trauma%2C%20often%20by%20someone%20the%20child%20knows%20and%20trusts%2C%20in%20places%20where%20they%20should%20feel%20safe.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pervasive%20nature%20of%20childhood%20sexual%20violence%20spans%20across%20cultural%2C%20geographical%2C%20and%20economic%20divides.%20The%20report%20highlights%20Sub-Saharan%20Africa%20as%20the%20region%20with%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20victims%2C%20accounting%20for%2079%20million%20affected%20women%20and%20girls.%20Other%20affected%20regions%20include%20Eastern%20and%20South-Eastern%20Asia%20(75%20million)%2C%20Central%20and%20Southern%20Asia%20(73%20million)%2C%20Europe%20and%20Northern%20America%20(68%20million)%2C%20and%20Latin%20America%20and%20the%20Caribbean%20(45%20million).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20regions%20marred%20by%20conflict%20and%20political%20instability%2C%20the%20situation%20is%20even%20more%20dire.%20Girls%20in%20fragile%20settings%2C%20such%20as%20refugee%20camps%20or%20areas%20under%20UN%20peacekeeping%20missions%2C%20face%20a%20higher%20risk%2C%20with%20sexual%20violence%20affecting%20more%20than%201%20in%204%20girls.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20witnessing%20horrific%20sexual%20violence%20in%20conflict%20zones%2C%20where%20rape%20and%20gender-based%20violence%20are%20often%20used%20as%20weapons%20of%20war%2C%26quot%3B%20Russell%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20points%20to%20a%20disturbing%20trend%3A%20most%20sexual%20violence%20against%20children%20occurs%20during%20adolescence%2C%20with%20a%20significant%20spike%20between%20ages%2014%20and%2017.%20Victims%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20experience%20repeated%20abuse%2C%20emphasizing%20the%20need%20for%20targeted%20interventions%20to%20break%20the%20cycle%20of%20trauma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20long-term%20impacts%20of%20sexual%20violence%20can%20be%20devastating.%20Survivors%20often%20struggle%20with%20mental%20health%20issues%2C%20such%20as%20anxiety%20and%20depression%2C%20and%20are%20at%20increased%20risk%20of%20sexually%20transmitted%20infections%2C%20substance%20abuse%2C%20and%20difficulty%20forming%20healthy%20relationships.%20The%20trauma%20is%20further%20compounded%20when%20survivors%20delay%20disclosing%20their%20abuse%2C%20or%20never%20report%20it%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20girls%20and%20women%20make%20up%20the%20majority%20of%20victims%2C%20the%20report%20also%20notes%20that%20boys%20are%20similarly%20affected.%20Between%20240%20and%20310%20million%20boys%20and%20men%20have%20experienced%20sexual%20violence%20during%20childhood%2C%20with%20the%20number%20rising%20to%20530%20million%20when%20non-contact%20forms%20of%20abuse%20are%20included.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Global%20Ministerial%20Conference%20on%20Violence%20Against%20Children%20approaches%20next%20month%2C%20UNICEF%20calls%20for%20urgent%20international%20action.%20Key%20recommendations%20include%20changing%20harmful%20social%20norms%2C%20equipping%20children%20with%20information%20to%20report%20abuse%2C%20ensuring%20victims%20have%20access%20to%20support%20services%2C%20and%20strengthening%20legal%20frameworks%20to%20protect%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728633600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fqc1obs6_unicef-report-on-girl-child-sexual-violence_625x300_11_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Finternational-day-of-girl-child-2024-one-in-eight-girls-experiences-sexual-assault-before-turning-18-says-unicef-6765714%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22International%20Day%20Of%20Girl%20Child%202024%3A%20The%20report%20highlights%20that%20when%20%26quot%3Bnon-contact%26quot%3B%20forms%20of%20abuse%20-%20such%20as%20online%20harassment%20or%20verbal%20assault%20-%20are%20factored%20in%2C%20the%20number%20rises%20to%20650%20million%2C%20or%201%20in%205.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Finternational-day-of-girl-child-2024-one-in-eight-girls-experiences-sexual-assault-before-turning-18-says-unicef-6765714%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Blog%3A%20'Am%20I%20Becoming%20My%20Mother%3F'%2C%20And%20Other%20Odd%20Questions%20While%20Moving%20House%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F2lgnf33_moving_625x300_11_October_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%209%20a.m.%20on%20a%20Sunday%20when%20nine%20men%20barged%20into%20my%20house.%20Chaos%20followed.%20They%20spread%20out%20across%20rooms%2C%20bathrooms%2C%20and%20the%20kitchen%2C%20shoving%20whatever%20they%20could%20find%20into%20boxes%20that%20seemed%20terribly%20small%20to%20hold%20everything.%20But%20they%20persisted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAre%20there%20valuables%20in%20this%3F%26quot%3B%20one%20of%20them%20pointed%20to%20a%20box%20of%20faux%20jewellery%20we%20had%20forgotten%20in%20an%20almirah's%20corner.%20%26quot%3BNever%20mind%2C%20we%20are%20putting%20it%20in%20the%20bag%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said%20as%20I%20exchanged%20confused%20glances%20with%20my%20wife.%20We%20sighed%20and%20looked%20on%2C%20trusting%20the%20professionals%20with%20their%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPacking%20and%20moving%20houses%20is%20a%20nerve-wracking%20experience.%20It's%20a%20pain%20seldom%20spoken%20about.%20It's%20a%20heartbreak%20that%20B.%20Praak%20has%20yet%20to%20write%20a%20song%20for.%20It's%20a%20loss%20that%20is%20not%20usually%20equated%20to%20missing%20Coldplay's%20tickets%2C%20but%20it's%20'something%20just%20like%20this'.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20was%20moving%20from%20Noida%20to%20Delhi.%20While%20the%20new%20address%20is%20barely%20six%20kilometres%20away%2C%20it%20feels%20like%20several%20light-years%20-%20not%20merely%20because%20of%20the%20time-space%20dilating%20the%20Delhi-Noida%20border%20traffic%20jam.%20The%20reason%20is%20much%20closer%20to%20the%20heart%3B%20it's%20about%20home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20House%20That%20Grew%20With%20Me%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20I%20have%20been%20an%20OG%20'%3Cem%3Edilliwala%3C%2Fem%3E'%20since%20birth%2C%20I%20moved%20to%20Noida%20in%202022%20to%20stay%20close%20to%20work.%20I%20was%20a%20new%20dad%20and%20wanted%20to%20be%20just%20a%20phone%20call%20away.%20My%20wife%20had%20taken%20a%20career%20break.%20Our%20parents%20visited%20often.%20The%20house%20-%20albeit%20rented%20-%20grew%2C%20along%20with%20our%20daughter.%20We%20were%20taking%20baby%20steps%20in%20building%20a%20fresh%2C%20new%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20think%20that's%20what%20houses%20do.%20They%20just%20exist%20around%20you%20as%20structures%20that%20you%20fill%20with%20memories%2C%20materials%2C%20and%20moments%20-%20the%20collection%20of%20which%20you%20call%20home.%20And%20while%20it's%20easy%20to%20move%20and%20update%20your%20address%2C%20pulling%20away%20from%20this%20physical%20cocoon%20takes%20some%20emotional%20toll.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20remove%20framed%20pictures%20that%20you%20had%20precisely%20marked%20with%20a%20scratchy%20pen%2C%20strip%20the%20floor%20of%20rugs%20you%20were%20too%20lazy%20to%20pick%20and%20dust%2C%20and%20claw%20out%20the%20corners%20where%20you%20threw%20stuff%20to%20check%20back%20later%2C%20you%20realise%20the%20little%20things%20that%20made%20it%20work%2C%20that%20made%20it%20a%20place%20with%20a%20soul.%20It's%20an%20experience%20that%20makes%20you%20reflect.%20You%20wonder%20why%20you%20have%20accumulated%204%2C310%20plastic%20food%20takeaway%20boxes.%20Are%20you%20turning%20into%20your%20mother%3F%20The%20plastic%20bags%20packed%20into%20a%20bigger%20plastic%20bag%20hung%20on%20the%20kitchen%20door%20would%20want%20to%20say%20yes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20house%20-%20now%20ex-house%20-%20there%20was%20a%20vacant%20hall.%20I%20added%20a%20projector%20and%20seating%20space%2C%20installed%20ambient%20lighting%2C%20and%20built%20a%20cosy%20cinema%20space.%20It%20did%20not%20come%20together%20at%20once%2C%20but%20bits%20and%20pieces%20picked%20up%20from%20several%20places%20over%20several%20months%20came%20together%20to%20shape%20this%20place.%20With%20a%20growing%20child%2C%20the%20toys%20kept%20piling%20too.%20They%20took%20up%20a%20space%20of%20their%20own%20and%20suddenly%20reclaimed%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20house.%20It%20was%20a%20cherished%20space%2C%20a%20place%20where%20life%20thrived.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EJust%20Like%20That...%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20just%20like%20that%2C%20it%20was%20time%20to%20leave.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20wife%20was%20slowly%20returning%20to%20her%20professional%20life%2C%20so%20Delhi%20was%20a%20mutually%20convenient%20location.%20Of%20course%2C%20when%20we%20moved%20into%20my%20previous%20house%2C%20we%20always%20knew%20that%20it%20was%20not%20forever%2C%20that%20we'd%20be%20shifting%20somewhere%20e