ot%3BApproach%20Should%20Be%20Of%20Development%2C%20Not%20Expansion%26quot%3B%3A%20PM%20At%20East%20Asia%20Summit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENoting%20that%20conflicts%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20world%20are%20having%20the%20most%20negative%20impact%20on%20the%20countries%20of%20the%20Global%20South%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20Friday%20called%20for%20the%20restoration%20of%20peace%20and%20stability%20in%20Eurasia%20and%20West%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%2019th%20East%20Asia%20Summit%2C%20PM%20Modi%20also%20asserted%20that%20solutions%20to%20problems%20cannot%20come%20from%20the%20battlefield.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20a%20free%2C%20open%2C%20inclusive%2C%20prosperous%20and%20rule-based%20Indo-Pacific%20is%20important%20for%20the%20peace%20and%20progress%20of%20the%20entire%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeace%2C%20security%20and%20stability%20of%20the%20South%20China%20Sea%20is%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20entire%20Indo-Pacific%20region%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20believe%20that%20maritime%20activities%20should%20be%20conducted%20under%20the%20UN%20Convention%20on%20the%20Law%20of%20the%20Seas%20(UNCLOS).%20It%20is%20necessary%20to%20ensure%20freedom%20of%20navigation%20and%20air%20space.%20A%20strong%20and%20effective%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20should%20be%20created.%20And%20it%20should%20not%20curb%20the%20foreign%20policy%20of%20regional%20countries%2C%E2%80%9D%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20approach%20should%20be%20one%20of%20developmentalism%20and%20not%20expansionism%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoting%20that%20the%20conflicts%20going%20on%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20world%20are%20having%20the%20most%20negative%20impact%20on%20the%20countries%20of%20the%20Global%20South%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%20everyone%20wants%20whether%20it%20is%20Eurasia%20or%20West%20Asia%2C%20peace%20and%20stability%20should%20be%20restored%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20come%20from%20the%20land%20of%20Buddha%2C%20and%20I%20have%20repeatedly%20said%20that%20this%20is%20not%20the%20era%20of%20war.%20Solutions%20to%20problems%20cannot%20come%20from%20the%20battlefield%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20necessary%20to%20respect%20sovereignty%2C%20territorial%20integrity%20and%20international%20laws.%20Keeping%20a%20humanitarian%20approach%2C%20dialogue%20and%20diplomacy%20will%20have%20to%20be%20given%20priority%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20prime%20minister%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFulfilling%20the%20responsibility%20of%20%E2%80%98Vishwabandhu'%2C%20India%20will%20continue%20to%20contribute%20in%20every%20possible%20way%20in%20this%20direction%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20remarks%20came%20amidst%20conflicts%20between%20Ukraine%20and%20Russia%20in%20Eurasia%20and%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war%20in%20West%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTerrorism%20is%20also%20a%20serious%20challenge%20to%20global%20peace%20and%20security.%20To%20face%20it%2C%20forces%20believing%20in%20humanity%20will%20have%20to%20work%20together%2C%E2%80%9D%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20start%20of%20his%20address%2C%20he%20also%20expressed%20his%20deepest%20condolences%20to%20the%20people%20affected%20by%20%E2%80%9CTyphoon%20Yagi%E2%80%9D%2C%20a%20destructive%20tropical%20cyclone%20which%20impacted%20Southeast%20Asia%20and%20South%20China%20in%20September%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20this%20difficult%20time%2C%20we%20have%20provided%20humanitarian%20assistance%20through%20Operation%20Sadbhav%2C%E2%80%9D%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20also%20said%20India%20has%20always%20supported%20ASEAN%20Unity%20and%20Centrality%20and%20pointed%20out%20that%20ASEAN%20is%20also%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20India's%20Indo-Pacific%20vision%20and%20Quad%20cooperation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20deep%20similarities%20between%20India's%20%E2%80%98Indo-Pacific%20Oceans'%20Initiative'%20and%20%E2%80%98ASEAN%20Outlook%20on%20Indo-Pacific'%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20support%20the%20ASEAN%20approach%20to%20the%20situation%20in%20Myanmar.%20We%20also%20support%20the%20Five-point%20Consensus.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20we%20believe%20that%20it%20is%20important%20to%20maintain%20humanitarian%20assistance%2C%E2%80%9D%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20called%20for%20appropriate%20steps%20for%20the%20restoration%20of%20democracy%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20believe%20that%2C%20for%20this%2C%20Myanmar%20should%20be%20engaged%2C%20not%20isolated%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20neighbouring%20country%2C%20India%20will%20continue%20to%20fulfil%20its%20responsibility%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20East%20Asia%20Summit%20is%20an%20important%20pillar%20of%20India's%20Act%20East%20Policy%2C%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728632940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fjvlt6smo_pm-modi-19th-east-asia-summit-_625x300_11_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-calls-for-peace-in-eurasia-west-asia-this-is-not-the-era-of-war-6764956%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Noting%20that%20conflicts%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20world%20are%20having%20the%20most%20negative%20impact%20on%20the%20countries%20of%20the%20Global%20South%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20Friday%20called%20for%20the%20restoration%20of%20peace%20and%20stability%20in%20Eurasia%20and%20West%20Asia.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-calls-for-peace-in-eurasia-west-asia-this