ing%20India%E2%80%99s%20Growth%20Story%20in%20Villages%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20This%20article%20features%20portfolio%C2%A0companies%20of%20Elevar%20Equity%2C%20which%C2%A0is%20also%20an%20investor%20in%20The%20Better%20India.%20Editorial%20integrity%20and%20transparency%20remain%20our%20priority%2C%20and%20this%20piece%20has%20been%20written%20independently%20to%20provide%20an%20unbiased%20view.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20truly%20comprehend%20the%20vast%20economic%20potential%20brimming%20in%20India%2C%20visit%20its%20rural%20heartlands%20%E2%80%93%20like%20driving%20through%20the%20villages%20of%20Hubbali%20district%20in%20Karnataka.%20As%20you%20negotiate%20the%20twists%20and%20turns%20of%20the%20road%2C%20notice%20how%20the%20verdant%20landscape%20is%20punctuated%20with%20shops%2C%20now%20and%20then.%20A%20closer%20look%20will%20reveal%20barcodes%20displayed%20in%20plain%20sight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20new%20addition%2C%20as%20shop%20owner%20Ishwargowda%20Basavanagowda%20Patil%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMonday%20mornings%20are%20a%20busy%20time%20for%20him%20and%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekirana%20%3C%2Fem%3E(general%20store)%20that%20he%20runs.%20But%20Ishwargowda%20seems%20unfazed%20by%20the%20slew%20of%20orders.%20He%E2%80%99s%20no%20longer%20required%20to%20ace%20mental%20math%20while%20attempting%20to%20calculate%20the%20amount%20of%20change%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20returned%20to%20a%20customer.%20UPI%20(Unified%20Payments%20Interface)%20has%20his%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20fascinating%20to%20watch%20the%20rhythmic%20order%20of%20business%20%E2%80%94%20with%20transactions%20happening%20in%20seconds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20picture%20of%20a%20new%20age%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20%5BUPI%5D%20makes%20things%20hassle-free%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ishwargowda%20points%20out.%20However%2C%20building%20a%20successful%20business%20requires%20a%20lot%20more%20than%20integrating%20tech%20into%20transactions%2C%20he%20emphasises.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20loans%20too.%E2%80%9D%20This%20is%20where%20SarvaGram%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20rural%20lending%20startups%20comes%20into%20play.%20A%20month%20ago%2C%20an%20opportunity%20knocked%20on%20Ishwargowda%E2%80%99s%20door%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20visit%20from%20one%20of%20SarvaGram%E2%80%99s%20staff%2C%20offering%20him%20a%20loan%20that%20would%20essentially%20take%20the%20business%20to%20new%20heights%2C%20by%20helping%20Ishwargowda%20purchase%20more%20stocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECynical%20at%20first%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20%E2%80%9Ctake%20a%20chance%E2%80%9D.%20And%20the%20results%20are%20reflected%20in%20his%20earnings%20today.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20income%20from%20the%20shop%20is%20between%20Rs%202%2C000%20to%20Rs%203%2C000%20per%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiles.%20That%20isn%E2%80%99t%20all.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20loan%20lets%20me%20grow%20my%20business%2C%20keep%20more%20stocks%20in%20my%20shop%2C%20and%20sell%20more%20things%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes%2C%20adding%20that%20as%20one%20of%20the%20only%20%3Cem%3Ekirana%20%3C%2Fem%3Eshops%20in%20the%20Amargol%20area%2C%20the%20demand%20is%20always%20burgeoning%20and%20the%20loan%20is%20helping%20him%20meet%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurial-households-2-1728368718.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22By%20integrating%20UPI%20into%20his%20business%20operations%2C%20Ishwargowda%20Basavanagowda%20Patil%20is%20able%20to%20carry%20out%20seamless%20operations%20at%20his%20kirana%20shop%20in%20Hubbali%2C%20Karnataka%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurial-households-2-1728368718.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.co