0the%20realities%20of%20these%20%5Brural%5D%20markets.%20We%20intended%20to%20target%20underbanked%20but%20creditworthy%20homes%2C%E2%80%9D%20Utpal%20notes.%20Together%20with%20Sameer%20Mishra%2C%20who%20has%20over%2020%20years%20of%20experience%20in%20rural%20finance%2C%20he%20founded%20SarvaGram%20%E2%80%94%20which%20has%20changed%20many%20lives%20like%20Ishwargowda%E2%80%99s%20with%20access%20to%20credit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20%5BSarvaGram%5D%20isn%E2%80%99t%20an%20overnight%20dream%2C%20but%20instead%2C%20a%20continuing%20success%20story%2C%E2%80%9D%20Utpal%20points%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGiving%20rural%20households%20agency%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Ishwargowda%E2%80%99s%20creditworthiness%20were%20to%20be%20assessed%20solely%20based%20on%20his%20income%20at%20the%20time%2C%20or%20his%20discretionary%20expenses%2C%20he%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20made%20the%20cut.%20A%20lack%20of%20steady%20income%20was%20why%20he%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20considered%20for%20a%20formal%20bank%20loan.%20To%20this%20end%2C%20when%20Utpal%20set%20out%20to%20conceive%20SarvaGram%2C%20he%20was%20keen%20to%20build%20it%20with%20a%20growth-oriented%20ethos%20that%20would%20provide%20loans%20to%20those%20with%20variable%20incomes%2C%20but%20aspirational%20mindsets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20as%20%E2%80%9CIndia%E2%80%99s%20first%20household-centric%2C%20data-led%2C%20%E2%80%98high-tech%20high-touch%E2%80%99%20distribution%20platform%E2%80%9D%2C%20SarvaGram%20is%20extending%20a%20hand%20towards%20rural%20India%20through%20its%20bouquet%20of%20financial%20and%20productivity-enhancing%20offerings.%20The%20cornerstone%20of%20the%20organisation%E2%80%99s%20services%20has%20been%20a%20keen%20focus%20on%20the%20%E2%80%9Cunderbanked%20but%20creditworthy%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FUyhbciwOdQ8%3Fsi%