0of%20local%20communities%20who%20lose%20their%20livestock%2C%20particularly%20sheep%20and%20goats%2C%20to%20these%20elusive%20creatures%3F%20To%20answer%20this%20question%2C%20he%20established%20the%20Snow%20Leopard%20Conservancy-India%20Trust%20(SLC-IT)%20in%202000%20to%20promote%20local%20efforts%20towards%20community-based%20conservation%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20taking%20a%20variety%20of%20steps%20to%20help%20local%20farmers%20and%20nomads%20protect%20their%20livestock%20from%20snow%20leopards%2C%20thus%20preventing%20man-animal%20conflicts%2C%20he%20also%20pioneered%20one%20of%20the%20earliest%20models%20of%20eco-tourism%20with%20conservation-linked%20homestays%20located%20in%20critical%20snow%20leopard%20habitats%20and%20along%20popular%20trekking%20routes.%20These%20successful%20models%20of%20community-based%20tourism%20in%20the%20Hemis%20National%20Park%2C%20the%20Sham%20region%2C%20and%20Zanskar%20still%20stand%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20tragically%20passed%20away%20at%20the%20age%20of%20just%2042%20in%202011%20due%20to%20a%20deteriorating%20neurological%20condition%20but%20not%20before%20leaving%20behind%20a%20stellar%20legacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Fateh%20Singh%20Rathore%3A%20The%20forest%20officer%20who%20showed%20India%20how%20to%20protect%20tigers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKnown%20for%20his%20trademark%20long%20handlebar%20moustache%2C%20olive-coloured%20safari%20hat%20and%20dashing%20dark%20glasses%2C%20the%20late%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F234711%2Fhow-does-india-protect-tigers-fateh-singh-rathore-ranthambhore-national-park-rajasthan-india-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFateh%20Singh%20Rathore%3C%2Fa%3E%20remains%20the%20principal%20architect%20behind%20the%20success%20story%20that%20is%20the%20Ranthambhore%20National%20Park.%20As%20a%20ranger%2C%20warden%2C%20and%20field%20director%20at%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20best-known%20tiger%20preserves%2C%20Fateh%E2%80%99s%20work%20emphasised%20three%20things%20%E2%80%94%20natural%20regeneration%20of%20the%20habitat%2C%20constant%20engagement%20with%20local%20communities%20living%20in%20its%20vicinity%20that%20went%20way%20beyond%20consultations%2C%20and%20an%20abiding%20love%20for%20the%20creatures%20who%20inhabited%20this%20forest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20became%20the%20blueprint%20for%20what%20a%20successful%20tiger%20conservation%20strategy%20looks%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F05103523%2FFateh_Singh_Rathore_2008-500x693.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Fateh%20Singh%20Rathore%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-234723%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22693%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EFateh%20Singh%20Rathore%20(Image%20courtesy%20Wikimedia%20Commons)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFateh%E2%80%99s%20approach%20to%20conservation%20was%20marked%20by%20his%20incredible%20knowledge%20of%20the%20terrain%20inside%20Ranthambore%E2%80%99s%20core%20area%20and%20the%20depth%20of%20his%20engagement%20with%20the%20local%20community%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20it%20was%20relocating%2016%20villages%20inhabited%20in%20the%20core%20area%20of%20the%20National%20Park%20and%20ensuring%20that%20the%20village%20economy%20thrived%20despite%20this%20resettlement%20and%20a%20crackdown%20on%20poaching.%20He%20nearly%20died%20for%20his%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20as%20a%20forest%20officer%2C%20his%20loyalties%20only%20lay%20with%20the%20forests%20and%20not%20politicians%20or%20superior%20officers%20%E2%80%94%20a%20feature%20of%20his%20work%20that%20would%20come%20at%20a%20great%20personal%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Jamal%20Ara%3A%20The%20first%20%E2